::Mosquitor::

On his way to the bridge, Mosquitor passes the entrance of the Predacon base, 
stopping as he feels vibrations. He frowns, walking over to the door. 
Mosquitor presses a button, the entrance opening. He jumps when he sees the 
bot were Maximal, opening fire at them with his acid gun, the autoguns of the 
ship also opening fire.
